data.title: The Process of Land Development in Sarawak
data.meta_description: The Process of Land Development in Sarawak - Free download as Word Doc (.doc), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document discusses land development in Sarawak, focusing on residential development projects undertaken by the government. It defines land development and describes the three main categories: commercial, industrial, and residential. It then discusses the rationale for Sarawak's government-led resettlement schemes, which aimed to address illegal squatting. Under the Seventh and Eighth Malaysia Plans, the government approved numerous resettlement projects across Sarawak's divisions. As of December 2003, 76 projects had been completed.
